Jamal, uhvati!

75
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:44,091
Jamal, tvoja je!

76
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:53,646
Kako si uspEo ispustiti tako
dobru loptu?

77
00:06:53,681 --> 00:06:56,257
Privatni aerodrom!

78
00:06:58,535 --> 00:07:00,269
Uhvati ga!

79
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:05,027
Psi dolaze! Beži!

80
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:11,059
Ako vas avioni ne ubiju, mi Cemo!

81
00:07:14,535 --> 00:07:16,724
Hej brate!

82
00:08:45,535 --> 00:08:47,830
Žao mi je!

83
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,077
Jako mi je žao.

84
00:09:02,845 --> 00:09:04,559
Oh sranje, to je mama.

85
00:09:04,594 --> 00:09:06,004
HoCeš li da te prebijem na
mrtvo ime, ha?

86
00:09:07,535 --> 00:09:10,448
Brate, ostavi ova dva meni.

87
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,988
Idemo.

88
00:09:16,868 --> 00:09:18,501
Athos.

89
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,736
Tri mušketira.

90
00:09:25,737 --> 00:09:29,540
Ponovi! "Zvali ste me, gospodine?"
rekao je Athos.

91
00:09:31,861 --> 00:09:35,009
Ah, dolaze naši pravi mušketiri.

92
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:38,615
Hvala Vam što ste nas poCastili
svojom prisutnošCu.

93
00:09:39,535 --> 00:09:40,670
Porthos!

94
00:09:40,705 --> 00:09:42,335
Pa, otvori, Salim.

95
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,831
Prestani to raditi i otvori
knjigu, Jamal.

96
00:09:48,935 --> 00:09:49,749
Athos?

97
00:10:08,979 --> 00:10:11,726
Onda... g. Malik

98
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:15,048
Covek koji zna sve odgovore.

99
00:10:17,536 --> 00:10:18,466
PriCaj.

100
00:10:20,137 --> 00:10:21,650
Govori!

101
00:10:26,774 --> 00:10:30,731
Onda, Jamal, jesi li spreman za
prvo pitanje, za 1000 rupija?

102
00:10:31,535 --> 00:10:33,465
Da.

103
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,500
Nije loše za samo sediti
na stolici

104
00:10:34,535 --> 00:10:36,465
i odgovarati na pitanje.

105
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:39,500
Bolje nego praviti caj, zar ne?

106
00:10:39,535 --> 00:10:41,465
Ne. Da. Ne.

107
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:46,000
Ne? Da? Ne? Je li to tvoj
konacni odgovor?

108
00:10:46,035 --> 00:10:50,500
Zapamti. Imaš tri pomoci.

109
00:10:50,535 --> 00:10:54,500
Pitaj publiku, pola-pola

110
00:10:54,535 --> 00:10:56,465
i pozovi prijatelja.

111
00:10:56,500 --> 00:11:00,359
Prvo pitanje, za 1000 rupija,
idemo.

112
00:11:00,535 --> 00:11:07,357
ko je bio glavna zvezda u filmu
iz 1973., "Zanjeer"?

113
00:11:17,535 --> 00:11:19,192
Gusto mi je ovdje...

114
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:25,499
Evo... Novac. Uzmi novac...

115
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:32,500
Izlazi, Jamal.
Prakash mora na veliku nuždu.

116
00:11:33,535 --> 00:11:36,499
Nisam gotov.

117
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:38,632
Pregrizi. Ovo je hitno...

118
00:11:38,633 --> 00:11:40,826
Ide polako van...

119
00:11:40,827 --> 00:11:43,619
i od kada postoji vremensko
ogranicenje za sranje?

120
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:46,465
Pri kraju sam, mali. Požuri...

121
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:50,500
Mušterija ceka,
požuri Jamal!

122
00:11:50,535 --> 00:11:53,500
Vrati mi novac!
Daj! Idem na drugo mesto.

123
00:11:53,535 --> 00:11:56,465
Glupi idiot.

124
00:11:56,500 --> 00:12:00,500
Koštao si me mušterije.

125
00:12:00,535 --> 00:12:03,465
Amitabhov helikopter!

126
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:04,735
To je Amitabhov helikopter!

127
00:12:05,333 --> 00:12:06,205
Amitabh!

128
00:12:08,422 --> 00:12:10,920
Amitabh Bachchan!

129
00:12:26,736 --> 00:12:27,780
Salim, otvori!

130
00:13:09,009 --> 00:13:11,154
Amitabh Bachchan!

131
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,377
Amitabh, gospodine!

132
00:13:30,129 --> 00:13:31,737
Makni se! makni se s puta!

133
00:13:31,772 --> 00:13:34,283
Molim te cekaj, dolazim!

134
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:39,346
Amitabh, gospodine,
dajte mi molim Vas autogram.

135
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:07,440
Imaš ga sad, zar ne?
Amitabhov autogram?

136
00:14:43,573 --> 00:14:46,161
To je bio moj autogram!

137
00:14:46,196 --> 00:14:48,210
Amitabh mi ga je dao!

138
00:14:48,311 --> 00:14:50,019
Nikad necu dobiti još jedan!

139
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:53,534
Ponudio je dobru cenu, pas
sam ga prodao.

140
00:14:53,602 --> 00:14:55,830
Ali bio je moj...

141
00:14:57,052 --> 00:15:00,465
A, Amitabh Bachchan.

142
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:03,486
Znaš što, u pravu si. Upravo
si osvojio 1,000 rupija.

143
00:15:07,535 --> 00:15:08,981
Ne treba biti genije.

144
00:15:09,093 --> 00:15:11,575
Znao sam da je to Amitabh Bachchan.

145
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:16,003
Kao što sam rekao, ne treba
biti genije.

146
00:15:19,535 --> 00:15:21,406
On je najpoznatiji covek u
Indiji.

147
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:27,567
Slika tri lava koja stoji na
nacionalnom grbu Indije.

148
00:15:28,535 --> 00:15:30,938
Što piše ispod?

149
00:15:31,552 --> 00:15:34,543
A: Samo istina pobeđuje

150
00:15:34,578 --> 00:15:37,762
B: Samo laž pobjeđuje

151
00:15:38,052 --> 00:15:40,622
C: Samo moda pobeđuje

152
00:15:41,428 --> 00:15:45,031
D: Samo novac pobeđuje

153
00:15:50,164 --> 00:15:51,965
Što ti misliš, Jamal?

154
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:56,410
Najpoznatija fraza u našoj zemlji.

155
00:15:56,535 --> 00:15:58,950
Želiš li pozvati prijatelja?

156
00:15:58,985 --> 00:16:01,465
Pitao bih publiku.

157
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:04,465
ko ce mu skratiti muke,
dame i gospodo?

158
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:07,500
Moja petogodišnja cerka zna
odgovor na to pitanje,

159
00:16:07,535 --> 00:16:08,887
ali ti nisi znao.

160
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:11,721
To je jako cudno za milionara
genija.

161
00:16:12,535 --> 00:16:13,986
Što se dogodilo?

162
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:17,500
Tvoj saucesnik je izašao 
na pišanje?

163
00:16:17,535 --> 00:16:20,465
Inspektor te je nešto pitao.

164
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:23,632
Koliko košta panipuri u
Dharisha ducanu na Chowpattyu?

165
00:16:24,430 --> 00:16:25,839
Šta?

166
00:16:25,874 --> 00:16:29,330
Panipuri. Jedna plata. Koliko?

167
00:16:29,535 --> 00:16:31,534
10 rupija. -Krivo.

168
00:16:31,535 --> 00:16:32,521
15, od Diwalia.

169
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:37,134
ko je Varmyu ukrao bicikl

170
00:16:37,135 --> 00:16:39,847
blizu Santa Cruz stanice
prošli četvrtak?

171
00:16:41,535 --> 00:16:42,906
Znaš ko je to bio?

172
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,500
Svatko u Juhuu zna to.

173
00:16:45,535 --> 00:16:48,355
Cak i petogodišnjaci.

174
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:55,453
Cestitam, Jamal.
Osvojio si 4,000 rupija.

175
00:17:00,535 --> 00:17:02,785
16 hiljada rupija.

176
00:17:05,052 --> 00:17:08,478
Religija. Zanimljivo.

177
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:12,216
Utelovljenje Boga Rame

178
00:17:12,217 --> 00:17:15,869
u svojoj desnoj ruci drži šta?

179
00:18:01,236 --> 00:18:04,512
Beži!

180
00:18:09,289 --> 00:18:11,057
Salim, Jamal! Bežite!

181
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,586
Oni su Muslimani, sredite ih!

182
00:19:12,784 --> 00:19:15,211
Beži! Beži sa nama!

183
00:19:25,715 --> 00:19:27,350
Hej, gubi se!

184
00:19:27,351 --> 00:19:30,822
Jesi li gluv? Rekao sam gubi se!

185
00:19:35,535 --> 00:19:37,366
Dođi sa nama.

186
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:54,040
Budim se svako jutro sa željom da
nisam znao odgovor na to pitanje.

187
00:19:57,535 --> 00:20:01,500
Da nije bilo Rame i Alaha...

188
00:20:01,535 --> 00:20:05,024
još uvijek bi imao majku.

189
00:20:14,365 --> 00:20:16,149
Luk i strela.

190
00:20:16,603 --> 00:20:17,826
Konačni odgovor?

191
00:20:20,363 --> 00:20:21,555
Konacni odgovor.

192
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:26,668
Kompjuter, D?

193
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:34,750
Osvojio si 16,000 rupija.

194
00:20:36,638 --> 00:20:38,857
Jako dobro, prijatelju.

195
00:20:41,147 --> 00:20:43,623
Vreme za reklame.
Nemojte otici.

196
00:20:45,535 --> 00:20:47,465
Imao si sreće, ha?

197
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:49,761
Da sam na tvom mestu, uzeo bih
novac i otišao.

198
00:20:50,535 --> 00:20:52,565
Neceš ici dalje.

199
00:21:26,535 --> 00:21:27,999
Beži!

200
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,190
Dovešcu  ovde osiguranje!

201
00:21:30,191 --> 00:21:31,599
Pusti je unutra.

202
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:35,962
Ona može biti treci mušketir.

203
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:41,391
Ja sam sad najstariji, i ja
kažem da ona ne ulazi, u redu?

204
00:21:42,535 --> 00:21:43,499
U svakom slucaju...

205
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:47,539
Cak niti ne znamo ime treceg
prokletog mušketira.

206
00:22:07,692 --> 00:22:09,038
Salim?

207
00:22:25,535 --> 00:22:27,207
Dođi ovde.

208
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,411
Gdje ti je majka?

209
00:22:44,535 --> 00:22:46,430
Otac?

210
00:22:50,156 --> 00:22:51,650
Ja sam Jamal.

211
00:22:51,685 --> 00:22:53,980
Ovo je moj brat, Salim.

212
00:22:55,535 --> 00:22:57,392
Ja sam Latika.

213
00:22:57,500 --> 00:23:00,409
Možeš spavati ovde ako želiš.

214
00:23:07,535 --> 00:23:09,487
Hvala ti, Jamal.

215
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:27,644
Dobrodošli natrag u "Milionera".

216
00:23:27,679 --> 00:23:31,500
Naš takmicar, Jamal Malik,
pomocnik u pozivnom centru iz Mumbaya,

217
00:23:31,535 --> 00:23:33,077
je na 16 hiljada rupija,

218
00:23:33,506 --> 00:23:36,822
i do sada je iskoristio samo
jednu pomoc, pitaj publiku.

219
00:23:38,535 --> 00:23:42,138
Onda, moj prijatelju, ideš na
ozbiljne novce.

220
00:23:43,535 --> 00:23:45,294
Hocemo li igrati dalje?

221
00:23:45,535 --> 00:23:47,015
Da.

222
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:57,500
Pesmu "Darshan Do Ghanshyam" je
napisao koji poznati Indijski pisac?

223
00:23:57,535 --> 00:24:00,017
A: Surdas

224
00:24:00,052 --> 00:24:02,276
B: Tulsidas

225
00:24:02,311 --> 00:24:04,108
C: Mira Bai

226
00:24:04,538 --> 00:24:06,812
D: Kabir

227
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,448
Vruce je, ha?

228
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:04,752
Nacin kako se odnosi prema nama,
sigurno je dobar covek.

229
00:26:04,753 --> 00:26:06,499
Sigurno je prokleti svetac.

230
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:08,775
Ne smemo pricati među sobom.

231
00:26:08,776 --> 00:26:10,499
Zašto?

232
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:14,917
Ako dobijemo repete, onda
je sigurno svetac.

233
00:26:34,535 --> 00:26:37,402
Jako dobro, Arvind. Jako dobro.

234
00:26:50,538 --> 00:26:53,134
Smeješ mi se. Ubicu te.

235
00:26:53,135 --> 00:26:55,551
Hej, pusti je.

236
00:26:55,952 --> 00:26:57,960
Ne diraj me!

237
00:26:57,961 --> 00:26:59,530
Ti debeli prokletnice!

238
00:27:01,826 --> 00:27:03,467
Ti veliko drvo!

239
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:05,930
Punnoose, mislim da smo 
našli psa.

240
00:27:19,535 --> 00:27:23,056
U redu, idemo. Vreme je za posao.

241
00:27:31,259 --> 00:27:33,107
Mislite da ste došli ovde
na piknik?

242
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:37,368
Što mislite da su ovo, praznici?

243
00:27:39,535 --> 00:27:42,291
A zašto se ti smeješ?

244
00:27:46,135 --> 00:27:47,665
Daj mi to.

245
00:27:52,591 --> 00:27:53,303
Cuti!

246
00:27:54,029 --> 00:27:54,763
Brat Salim.

247
00:27:55,291 --> 00:27:57,176
Šta je, mali brate, imaš problema?

248
00:27:57,177 --> 00:27:59,175
Hej, uzmi je. Ona je tvoja danas.

249
00:27:59,176 --> 00:28:00,563
Ne želim je.

250
00:28:00,564 --> 00:28:03,707
Uzmi je. To je za tvoje dobro.
Bebe zarađuju duplo.

251
00:28:03,708 --> 00:28:06,035
Rekla je da je ne želi.

252
00:28:06,036 --> 00:28:07,012
Cuti, Jamal!

253
00:28:08,349 --> 00:28:10,839
Uzmi je odmah ili cu
je ispustiti.

254
00:28:15,435 --> 00:28:18,810
Neka nastavi da place, i zaradiceš
trostruko.

255
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:23,138
Hajde! Na posao!

256
00:28:48,535 --> 00:28:52,283
Uzecemo one najljuce.

257
00:29:46,145 --> 00:29:51,157
Chilli na pimpeku!

258
00:29:57,432 --> 00:29:59,032
Vraticu vam to!

259
00:30:00,776 --> 00:30:02,650
Vracajte se svi na spavanje!

260
00:30:27,535 --> 00:30:30,919
Jako dobro. Sretan sam.

261
00:30:31,717 --> 00:30:35,041
Spreman je. -I ja sam spreman.

262
00:30:50,535 --> 00:30:52,346
Hajde, približi lampu.

263
00:31:36,535 --> 00:31:38,315
U redu.

264
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:46,214
Dovedi Jamala.

265
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:07,017
Slušaj, mali. Sad je vreme
da odluciš.

266
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:11,693
Želiš li život skitnice ili
život pravog coveka, ha?

267
00:32:11,728 --> 00:32:15,499
Pravog coveka. Revolveraša.

268
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:18,664
Sudbina ti je u rukama, covece.

269
00:32:19,535 --> 00:32:23,439
Možeš biti kao ja ili...

270
00:32:25,535 --> 00:32:26,890
Jesi li razumeo?

271
00:32:30,894 --> 00:32:32,111
Razumeo sam.

272
00:32:34,074 --> 00:32:36,434
Idi. Dovedi Jamala.

273
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:49,749
Samo mi treba da se Mamanu svidi
moje pevanje, i imacemo novca.

274
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:52,499
Puno novca, Latika.

275
00:32:52,500 --> 00:32:54,997
I onda šta? Možemo i prestati da
prosimo?

276
00:32:54,998 --> 00:32:57,413
Prositi? Šališ se?

277
00:32:57,414 --> 00:32:59,837
Živecemo u kuci u
Harbour Roadu.

278
00:32:59,838 --> 00:33:02,885
Ti, ja i Salim. Tri musketira.

279
00:33:02,886 --> 00:33:04,730
Harbour Road. Stvarno?

280
00:33:04,731 --> 00:33:06,024
Da.

281
00:33:08,500 --> 00:33:10,500
Na mesecini...

282
00:33:10,535 --> 00:33:11,465
Ti i ja.

283
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:14,472
Plesaceš sa mnom, hoceš li?

284
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:20,183
Nadam se da bolje pevaš
nego što plešeš.

285
00:33:25,535 --> 00:33:29,206
Moj je red. -Pevaj dobro.

286
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:38,757
Znaci to je to, ha, brate?

287
00:33:41,486 --> 00:33:43,889
Bolji živote, dolazimo.

288
00:33:45,535 --> 00:33:47,443
Athos.

289
00:33:48,890 --> 00:33:50,460
Porthos?

290
00:33:52,372 --> 00:33:54,214
Kad kažem.

291
00:34:10,904 --> 00:34:12,500
Vreme je postati profesionalac.

292
00:34:12,535 --> 00:34:14,465
Šta? Stvarno?

293
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:17,360
Prvo daj da cujem pesmu...

294
00:34:18,535 --> 00:34:21,388
Darshan to Ghanshyam.

295
00:34:22,167 --> 00:34:23,823
To mi je omiljena.

296
00:34:28,535 --> 00:34:31,835
Pedeset rupija.

297
00:34:35,253 --> 00:34:37,230
Sad sam profesionalac,
šta mogu?

298
00:34:37,822 --> 00:34:39,013
Prepredenjak.

299
00:34:41,664 --> 00:34:43,474
Evo ga.

300
00:35:04,361 --> 00:35:07,059
Jamal, beži!

301
00:35:07,094 --> 00:35:09,189
Uhvatite ih!

302
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:15,333
Uzmite baklje! Uhvatite ih!

303
00:35:39,535 --> 00:35:41,571
Latika, beži!

304
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:16,311
Hajde, Latika! Uhvati mi ruku!

305
00:36:33,752 --> 00:36:35,814
Što se dogodilo, što se dogodilo?

306
00:36:35,849 --> 00:36:38,329
Pustila je!

307
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:48,534
Moramo se vratiti, brate.
Moramo se vratiti.

308
00:36:48,535 --> 00:36:50,534
Ako se vratimo, mrtvi smo.

309
00:36:50,535 --> 00:36:52,499
Jesi li poludeo?

310
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:56,289
Hteo je da ti izvadi oci!

311
00:36:56,290 --> 00:36:58,071
Sa žicom.

312
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:10,884
Ne brini se za nju.
Bice ona dobro.

313
00:37:11,535 --> 00:37:15,361
Uvek je bila dobro.

314
00:37:30,535 --> 00:37:34,083
Surdas.

315
00:37:40,276 --> 00:37:42,926
Surdas?

316
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:50,415
Surdas, konacni odgovor?

317
00:37:50,535 --> 00:37:52,689
Da.

318
00:37:56,500 --> 00:38:01,777
Znaš šta, u pravu si!

319
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:11,740
Slepi pevaci zarade duplo,
znaš li to?

320
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:15,856
Šta se dogodilo sa curom?
I nju su oslepili?

321
00:38:18,535 --> 00:38:21,312
Imali su druge planove.

322
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:25,845
Trebalo mi je dugo vremena
da saznam koje.

323
00:38:45,535 --> 00:38:47,465
Moraš to pustiti.

324
00:38:49,535 --> 00:38:51,535
Idemo.

325
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:55,394
Kuda? -Jako sam gladan.

326
00:40:12,035 --> 00:40:13,535
Diži se!

327
00:40:15,035 --> 00:40:18,035
Je li ti to tatin voz?

328
00:41:39,535 --> 00:41:43,268
Je li ovo raj?

329
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:48,755
Nisi mrtav, Jamal.

330
00:41:49,535 --> 00:41:51,551
Što je ovo?

331
00:41:51,552 --> 00:41:53,736
Neki hotel, ha?

332
00:41:54,500 --> 00:42:00,438
Taj Mahal je najlepši
primer moderne arhitekture.

333
00:42:04,250 --> 00:42:09,234
...završen je negde oko 1648.
uz pomoc oko 20,000 radnika.

334
00:42:09,568 --> 00:42:15,144
1980 je postao zašticen od
strane UNESCO-a...

335
00:42:26,535 --> 00:42:29,570
Službeni vodic.

336
00:42:29,605 --> 00:42:31,772
Molim Vas skinite cipele

337
00:42:49,535 --> 00:42:52,275
molim, molim.

338
00:42:52,276 --> 00:42:53,799
Kada je sledeca tura?

339
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:56,325
Nemamo baš puno vremena.

340
00:42:56,326 --> 00:42:57,937
Moramo još pogledati Red
Fort ovo poslepodne.

341
00:42:57,938 --> 00:42:59,499
POSETIOCI MORAJU UZETI
POTVRDU

342
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:03,399
Ne, ja... -Da li biste nas mogli
odmah provesti okolo?

343
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:09,382
Razumemo da ce koštati malo
više za samo nas dvoje.

344
00:43:09,383 --> 00:43:11,959
Ali naravno, gospođo!

345
00:43:12,589 --> 00:43:13,973
Molim Vas pratite me.

346
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:18,465
Taj Mahal je sagradio car
Khurrama

347
00:43:18,500 --> 00:43:24,000
za svoju ženu Mumtaz, koja je
bila najlepša žena na svetu.

348
00:43:24,035 --> 00:43:29,500
kada je ona umrla, car je
odlucio da napravi ovaj divan hotel,

349
00:43:29,535 --> 00:43:32,465
za svakoga ko se odluci posetiti
njenu grobnicu.

350
00:43:32,500 --> 00:43:38,500
Ali on je umro 1587. pre nego
što su napravljene sobe i liftovi.

351
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:45,500
Ali ovaj bazen koji vidite je bio
gotov na vreme, i jako moderan.

352
00:43:46,535 --> 00:43:49,465
U vodicu ne piše ništa o tome.

353
00:43:49,500 --> 00:43:55,500
Vodic su napisali bezvezni
Indijski prosjaci.

354
00:43:57,535 --> 00:44:02,500
A ovo, dame i gospodo, je
pocivalište od Mumtaz.

355
00:44:02,535 --> 00:44:05,465
Kako je umrla?

356
00:44:05,500 --> 00:44:08,000
Saobracajna nesreca. -Stvarno?

357
00:44:08,035 --> 00:44:10,465
Puno žrtava.

358
00:44:10,500 --> 00:44:14,465
Mislio sam da je umrla na porodaju.

359
00:44:14,500 --> 00:44:19,500
Tacno, gospodine. Bila je na
putu za bolnicu kad se to dogodilo.

360
00:44:25,535 --> 00:44:28,347
Spremni?

361
00:44:29,434 --> 00:44:30,843
osmeh.

362
00:44:37,977 --> 00:44:41,068
Cipele! Americke cipele!

363
00:45:02,535 --> 00:45:06,093
Osmeh.

364
00:45:18,500 --> 00:45:23,500
Ovo, g. David, je najveci
Dhobi Ghat u celoj Indiji.

365
00:45:23,535 --> 00:45:25,465
To je cudesno.

366
00:45:25,500 --> 00:45:28,500
Dođite, pogledajte ovo.

367
00:45:28,535 --> 00:45:31,465
Kažu da svaki covek u
Uttar Pradeshu

368
00:45:31,500 --> 00:45:37,500
nosi kurtu koja je barem
jednom bila oprana ovde.

369
00:45:43,871 --> 00:45:48,742
Brže malo! Brzina kao u pit-stopu
na trkama! Kao kod Schumachera!

370
00:45:49,500 --> 00:45:54,008
Jesu li to krave ili buffala...
Što je ono tamo?

371
00:46:02,535 --> 00:46:04,465
Oh, sranje.

372
00:46:04,500 --> 00:46:05,465
Što se to dovraga dogodilo
ovde?

373
00:46:14,535 --> 00:46:16,465
Stani malo!

374
00:46:16,500 --> 00:46:18,500
Imate osiguranje, zar ne?

375
00:46:18,895 --> 00:46:19,655
Jesi li dobro?

376
00:46:20,118 --> 00:46:22,696
Hteli ste videti pravu
Indiju? Ovo je to!

377
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:27,475
Evo malo i prave Amerike, sine.

378
00:46:28,048 --> 00:46:29,500
("Novac")

379
00:46:29,809 --> 00:46:31,135
Oh, da, da! Isuse...

380
00:46:34,511 --> 00:46:35,432
Evo.

381
00:48:19,348 --> 00:48:22,500
Na novcanici od 100 dolara

382
00:48:22,501 --> 00:48:26,625
je portret kojeg Americkog
državnika?

383
00:48:27,535 --> 00:48:30,551
A: George Washingtona

384
00:48:30,552 --> 00:48:34,060
B: Franklin Roosevelta

385
00:48:34,061 --> 00:48:37,583
C: Benjamin Franklina

386
00:48:37,584 --> 00:48:40,980
D: Abraham Lincolna

387
00:48:44,442 --> 00:48:48,965
Isplata ili igraš dalje, Jamal?

388
00:48:49,535 --> 00:48:52,335
Odluci.

389
00:48:52,500 --> 00:48:56,500
Bože, on gleda u kameru,
nema pojma koji je odgovor.

390
00:48:56,535 --> 00:48:59,517
Sad će otići. Budite spremni.

391
00:48:59,552 --> 00:49:02,500
Ne, prvo ce se malo
poigrati s njim.

392
00:49:02,535 --> 00:49:04,465
Jamal?

393
00:49:04,500 --> 00:49:09,650
Jesi li u svom poslu imao puno
kontakta s novcanicama od 100 dolara?

394
00:49:09,685 --> 00:49:13,465
Minimalna napojnica za
moje uslugu.

395
00:49:13,500 --> 00:49:16,500
Sad znam zašto su mi
racuni za mobilni tako visoki.

396
00:49:16,535 --> 00:49:20,500
Daju napojnice poslužitelju
od 100 dolara.

397
00:49:20,535 --> 00:49:23,017
Odgovor je C. Benjamin Franklin.

398
00:49:23,052 --> 00:49:25,465
Igraš dalje, ha?

399
00:49:25,500 --> 00:49:27,500
Mislim da upravo jesam, zar ne?

400
00:49:27,535 --> 00:49:29,517
Igrao si C, zar ne?

401
00:49:29,552 --> 00:49:31,500
ko je na novcanici
od 1,000 rupija?

402
00:49:31,535 --> 00:49:33,995
Ne znam.

403
00:49:34,552 --> 00:49:36,104
Ne znaš?

404
00:49:37,815 --> 00:49:39,225
Ghandi je.

405
00:49:40,192 --> 00:49:42,321
Oh, cuo sam za njega.

406
00:49:45,535 --> 00:49:46,465
Nemoj mi se praviti pametan

407
00:49:46,500 --> 00:49:49,500
jer cu ponovno doneti struju.

408
00:49:49,535 --> 00:49:51,465
Pogledaj.

409
00:49:51,500 --> 00:49:55,500
Nisu me pitali to pitanje.
ne znam zašto.

410
00:49:55,535 --> 00:49:57,465
Pitajte ih.

411
00:49:57,500 --> 00:50:03,500
Smiešno je, izgleda da te
baš ne zanima jako novac.

412
00:50:03,535 --> 00:50:06,607
Cinjenica je da imaš...

413
00:50:06,837 --> 00:50:11,018
jedan milion rupija!

414
00:50:14,447 --> 00:50:17,703
Objasni novcanicu od 100 dolara.

415
00:50:18,500 --> 00:50:22,846
Bombay je promenio ime
u Mumbay.

416
00:50:25,535 --> 00:50:27,354
Zašto ne razumeš?

417
00:50:58,500 --> 00:51:02,465
Djevojka je živjela ovdje.
Visoka je otprilike kao ja.

418
00:51:02,500 --> 00:51:06,519
Zvala se Latika.
Ne znam nikoga po tom imenu.

419
00:51:34,964 --> 00:51:39,090
Dva pileca burgera, dva pomfrita,
jedna dijetna kola, jedna coca cola!

420
00:51:39,091 --> 00:51:40,851
Jedna mineralna!

421
00:51:43,535 --> 00:51:45,478
Shimla.

422
00:51:46,500 --> 00:51:51,000
Idem u Chowpatty, ok?
Ideš sa mnom?

423
00:51:51,035 --> 00:51:55,500
Za ime Boga, jesi li zdrav?

424
00:51:55,535 --> 00:51:58,017
Silom želiš natrag u tu rupu.

425
00:51:58,052 --> 00:52:00,500
Ostavili smo naše prijatelje,
dobar život,

426
00:52:00,535 --> 00:52:02,517
puno novca. Zbog ovoga?!

427
00:52:02,552 --> 00:52:04,465
Vratili smo se da je nađemo.

428
00:52:04,500 --> 00:52:08,000
Ti si to napravio. Mene nije
briga za nju.

429
00:52:08,035 --> 00:52:11,500
Ima dosta pica u Bombayu
za Salima.

430
00:52:11,535 --> 00:52:12,465
Oh da!

431
00:52:12,500 --> 00:52:15,500
Trebao bi doci u Kaveze
u subotu uvece,

432
00:52:15,535 --> 00:52:19,500
umesto da tragaš za
svojom izgubljenom ljubavi.

433
00:52:19,535 --> 00:52:22,017
Idem u Chowpatty.

434
00:52:22,052 --> 00:52:24,465
Idem u Chowpatty!

435
00:52:24,500 --> 00:52:28,500
Ima 19 miliona ljudi u
ovom gradu, Jamal.

436
00:52:28,535 --> 00:52:31,500
Zaboravi na nju.

437
00:52:31,535 --> 00:52:34,989
Ona je "stree"(mlada Indijska
plesacica).

438
00:52:54,041 --> 00:52:55,540
Pozdrav, gospodine.

439
00:52:55,541 --> 00:52:59,488
Blagosloveni bili oni
koji cine dobro drugima.

440
00:53:08,535 --> 00:53:11,017
Dolari. Koliko?

441
00:53:11,018 --> 00:53:14,034
100. -Misliš da sam budala.

442
00:53:14,035 --> 00:53:17,440
Casna rec. Kunem se
dušom moje majke.

443
00:53:17,441 --> 00:53:23,940
Šta je na ovoj novcanici?
Cija je slika gore?

444
00:53:23,941 --> 00:53:26,465
Stari covek...

445
00:53:26,500 --> 00:53:30,500
Celav je na vrhu glave, sa dugom
kosom sa strane, kao curica.

446
00:53:30,535 --> 00:53:32,729
Benjamin Franklin.

447
00:53:37,500 --> 00:53:42,534
Sad si veliki decko, Jamal.

448
00:53:42,535 --> 00:53:45,017
Drago mi je zbog tebe.

449
00:53:45,052 --> 00:53:47,465
Oprosti...

450
00:53:47,500 --> 00:53:50,500
Spasio si mog prijatelja.
Ja nisam bio te srece.

451
00:53:50,535 --> 00:53:53,017
To je jedina razlika.

452
00:53:53,052 --> 00:53:55,276
Arvind, pokušavam naci...

453
00:53:55,311 --> 00:53:57,500
Dužan si Mamanu. Drži se dalje
od njega.

454
00:53:57,535 --> 00:53:59,960
On nikada ne zaboravlja.

455
00:53:59,961 --> 00:54:02,483
Dugujem Latiki.

456
00:54:04,500 --> 00:54:05,465
Živa je, zar ne?

457
00:54:05,500 --> 00:54:11,309
Više nego živa. Ona je u ulici
Pila. Zovu je Cherry.

458
00:54:13,535 --> 00:54:15,380
Hvala.

459
00:54:20,600 --> 00:54:22,698
Pevacu ti na sprovodu.

460
00:55:44,500 --> 00:55:48,286
Onda, je li to ona ili ne?

461
00:55:54,535 --> 00:55:57,050
Ona je seksi, covece!

462
00:56:03,500 --> 00:56:04,465
ko je to? -Jamal?

463
00:56:04,500 --> 00:56:07,500
Uzecu torbe.
-ko si ti? Šta želiš?

464
00:56:07,535 --> 00:56:10,500
Glupi decaci! -Pokupi to.

465
00:56:10,535 --> 00:56:12,535
Kako si me našao?

466
00:56:17,500 --> 00:56:18,765
Uzmi novac. Hajde!

467
00:56:18,766 --> 00:56:20,517
Imamo sve. Idemo!

468
00:56:21,500 --> 00:56:23,289
Sranje.

469
00:56:24,500 --> 00:56:27,531
Gle ko je to ovde!

470
00:56:29,139 --> 00:56:30,745
Pozdrav ponovo.

471
00:56:31,187 --> 00:56:35,781
Jamal, Salim.

472
00:56:36,810 --> 00:56:38,548
Nikad ne zaboravljam lice.

473
00:56:39,535 --> 00:56:40,465
Imam nos za to,

474
00:56:40,500 --> 00:56:43,819
posebno za one koje posedujem.

475
00:56:46,500 --> 00:56:52,500
Stvarno ste mislili da cete samo
doci i uzeti moje blago?

476
00:56:52,535 --> 00:56:55,230
Latika, dođi.

477
00:56:59,500 --> 00:57:05,271
Imate li pojma koliko ova mala
nevina curica vredi?

