Salim ce nam pomoci.

718
01:22:15,500 --> 01:22:21,358
Salim? Još uvek
veruješ u Salima?

719
01:22:24,342 --> 01:22:27,642
Jamal, uskoro cu otici.

720
01:22:27,677 --> 01:22:30,508
Odlazimo iz Bombaya.

721
01:22:31,535 --> 01:22:33,465
Gde?

722
01:22:33,500 --> 01:22:35,577
Misliš da ce mi reci?

723
01:22:36,524 --> 01:22:38,446
Ne! Ne! Ne!

724
01:22:58,500 --> 01:23:01,982
Kakvo je ovo sranje?

725
01:23:01,983 --> 01:23:05,823
Izlazi! Izlazi!

726
01:23:11,500 --> 01:23:16,465
Hajde, pre nego nas oboje ubije.

727
01:23:16,500 --> 01:23:19,500
Možeš li nešto napraviti
za mene? -Sve.

728
01:23:19,535 --> 01:23:21,500
Onda me zaboravi.

729
01:23:21,535 --> 01:23:23,465
Šta? Ne.

730
01:23:23,500 --> 01:23:30,500
Cekacu. VT stanica.
5 sati, svaki dan dok ne dođeš.

731
01:23:33,535 --> 01:23:36,465
Volim te.

732
01:23:36,500 --> 01:23:43,500
Pa šta onda?
Prekasno je, Jamal. Idi sada.

733
01:23:51,535 --> 01:23:52,465
Pa, Jamal.

734
01:23:52,500 --> 01:23:57,500
Koji igrac kriketa je napravio
najviše bodova u istoriji?

735
01:23:57,535 --> 01:23:59,517
A:Sachin Tendulkar

736
01:23:59,552 --> 01:24:02,026
B:Ricky Ponting

737
01:24:02,061 --> 01:24:05,780
C:Michael Slater

738
01:24:05,815 --> 01:24:09,465
D:Jack Hobbs

739
01:24:09,500 --> 01:24:14,500
Ali, zapamti, ako pogrešno odgovoriš,

740
01:24:14,535 --> 01:24:19,500
samo tako ceš izgubiti sve.

741
01:24:19,535 --> 01:24:26,535
Pa, da li želiš ovo odgovoriti?

742
01:24:46,723 --> 01:24:51,300
Toliko snova...

743
01:24:51,301 --> 01:24:52,974
na podu.

744
01:27:35,500 --> 01:27:39,500
Vreme je za reklame,
dame i gospodo.

745
01:27:39,535 --> 01:27:43,500
Znam, znam. Ni ja ne mogu
podneti pritisak.

746
01:27:43,535 --> 01:27:47,535
Vraticemo se odmah.

747
01:27:55,500 --> 01:28:00,500
Decko iz sirotinjskog kraja
postaje milioner preko noci.

748
01:28:00,535 --> 01:28:05,500
Znaš kome je to još
jedino uspelo?

749
01:28:05,535 --> 01:28:07,465
Meni.

750
01:28:09,500 --> 01:28:11,465
Znam kakav je to osecaj.

751
01:28:11,500 --> 01:28:14,465
Znam kroz šta prolaziš.

752
01:28:14,500 --> 01:28:17,500
Ja necu postati milioner.

753
01:28:17,535 --> 01:28:20,517
Ne znam odgovor.

754
01:28:20,552 --> 01:28:23,026
Rekao si to i pre, da...

755
01:28:23,061 --> 01:28:25,465
Stvarno, ovaj put ne znam.

756
01:28:25,500 --> 01:28:31,500
Hajde, ne možeš sada
uzeti lovu i pobeci.

757
01:28:31,535 --> 01:28:34,517
Ti si na pragu da uđeš u istoriju.

758
01:28:34,552 --> 01:28:38,026
Ne znam šta još mogu napraviti.

759
01:28:38,061 --> 01:28:41,465
Možda je to napisano, prijatelju.

760
01:28:41,500 --> 01:28:46,500
Imam neki osjecaj
da ceš ovo osvojiti.

761
01:28:46,535 --> 01:28:53,535
Veruj mi, Jamal.

762
01:29:05,052 --> 01:29:12,052
Osvojiceš ovo.

763
01:29:23,500 --> 01:29:26,378
Pripremite se svi.
U eteru smo za 13...

764
01:29:30,387 --> 01:29:32,016
Da, otišao je. Samo dajem...

765
01:29:34,313 --> 01:29:35,649
Hajde, brže.

766
01:29:36,500 --> 01:29:38,470
20 sekundi!

767
01:29:43,500 --> 01:29:45,500
Napravi pravu stvar i za,
oko 3 minuta,

768
01:29:45,535 --> 01:29:48,895
biceš popularan kao i ja.

769
01:29:48,896 --> 01:29:50,465
10 sekundi!

770
01:29:50,500 --> 01:29:55,500
I bogat kao i ja. Skoro kao ja.

771
01:29:55,535 --> 01:29:58,465
5 sekundi! 4... 3...

772
01:29:58,500 --> 01:30:02,832
Od siromaha do bogataša.
To je tvoja sudbina.

773
01:30:02,833 --> 01:30:08,337
U eteru smo.
Pljesak i muziku, molim!

774
01:30:18,966 --> 01:30:22,465
Dobro došli natrag u
"ko želi biti milioner?"!

775
01:30:22,500 --> 01:30:28,500
U stolici je veceras Jamal
Malik, kao da to ne znamo.

776
01:30:28,535 --> 01:30:32,017
Za 10 milijuna rupija.

777
01:30:32,052 --> 01:30:35,465
Treba ponovno odgovoriti.

778
01:30:35,500 --> 01:30:42,500
Koji igrac kriketa je napravio
najviše bodova u istoriji?

779
01:30:43,535 --> 01:30:45,500
Ne, to nije Sachin Tendulkar.

780
01:30:45,535 --> 01:30:47,465
To je pocetak.

781
01:30:47,500 --> 01:30:54,500
Pa, mogao bi biti Ricky Ponting,
Jack Hobbs ili Michael Slater.

782
01:30:54,535 --> 01:30:57,500
Iskoristicu pomoc. Pola-pola.

783
01:30:57,535 --> 01:30:59,465
Ok.

784
01:30:59,500 --> 01:31:05,500
Molim vas da odstranite
dva pogrešna odgovora.

785
01:31:05,535 --> 01:31:08,517
Pa, bio si u pravu
za Sachin Tendulkara.

786
01:31:08,552 --> 01:31:11,500
To ti ostavlja još dve
mogucnosti, Jamal.

787
01:31:11,535 --> 01:31:15,500
B: Ricky Ponting
ili D: Jack Hobbs.

788
01:31:15,535 --> 01:31:19,465
Šta misliš?

789
01:31:19,500 --> 01:31:25,500
Vreme odluke.
Za 10 miliona rupija.

790
01:31:25,535 --> 01:31:29,500
B: Ricky Ponting

791
01:31:29,501 --> 01:31:32,552
ili D: Jack Hobbs.

792
01:31:45,535 --> 01:31:51,017
D.

793
01:31:51,052 --> 01:31:56,465
Ne B?

794
01:31:56,500 --> 01:32:02,500
Ricky Ponting,
veliki Australski igrac kriketa?

795
01:32:02,535 --> 01:32:06,500
D, Jack Hobbs.

796
01:32:06,535 --> 01:32:11,465
Znaš?

797
01:32:11,500 --> 01:32:14,500
Pa, mogao bi biti B,
Ricky Ponting?

798
01:32:14,535 --> 01:32:19,017
Ili D, Jack Hobbs.

799
01:32:19,052 --> 01:32:23,465
Konacni odgovor, D.

800
01:32:23,500 --> 01:32:27,500
Kompjuter, D.

801
01:32:27,535 --> 01:32:34,535
D.

802
01:32:43,500 --> 01:32:50,500
Sa 197 bodova, odgovor je...

803
01:32:51,535 --> 01:32:58,465
D, Jack Hobbs!

804
01:32:58,500 --> 01:33:05,500
Jamal Malik! Milioner!

805
01:33:05,673 --> 01:33:12,673
Pleši! Hajde!

806
01:33:14,746 --> 01:33:17,597
Bravo! Bravo.

807
01:33:41,500 --> 01:33:45,500
Da li si spreman za zadnje pitanje?

808
01:33:45,535 --> 01:33:52,465
Za 20 miliona rupija.

809
01:33:52,500 --> 01:33:59,500
Ne. Ali možda je napisano.

810
01:33:59,535 --> 01:34:02,465
Možda.

811
01:34:02,500 --> 01:34:09,000
Ok. Zadnje pitanje!
Na "ko želi biti...

812
01:34:09,035 --> 01:34:15,500
Koji show, dame i gospodo!
Koji show!

813
01:34:15,535 --> 01:34:16,465
Pridružite nam se sutra uvece

814
01:34:16,500 --> 01:34:23,500
da vidite da li ce Jamal Malik
napraviti najvecu grešku u svom životu.

815
01:34:24,535 --> 01:34:31,517
Ovuda.

816
01:34:31,552 --> 01:34:38,465
Super show.

817
01:34:38,500 --> 01:34:39,900
Vidimo se sutra, ok.

818
01:34:39,935 --> 01:34:42,535
Dođi na vreme. 

819
01:34:53,052 --> 01:35:00,052
Što se događa?

820
01:35:00,500 --> 01:35:06,465
- On vara.
- Kako znaš da vara?

821
01:35:06,500 --> 01:35:11,500
Dao sam mu pogrešan
odgovor, a on je ispravno odgovorio.

822
01:35:11,535 --> 01:35:14,465
Dao si mu odgovor?

823
01:35:14,500 --> 01:35:20,500
Ne baš tako. Ali to sada nije
važno. To je moj show!

824
01:35:20,535 --> 01:35:27,535
Moj jebeni show!

825
01:35:33,500 --> 01:35:38,000
To je bizarno prihvatljivo,
ali ipak...

826
01:35:38,035 --> 01:35:42,500
Zato što sam iz sirotinjskog
kraja, poslužitelj,

827
01:35:42,535 --> 01:35:44,017
zato sam lažljivac?

828
01:35:44,052 --> 01:35:45,465
Vecina vas je.

829
01:35:45,500 --> 01:35:50,500
Ali ti nisi lažljivac, g. Malik.
To je sigurno.

830
01:35:50,535 --> 01:35:55,500
I previše si iskren.

831
01:35:55,535 --> 01:36:00,465
Gotovi smo.

832
01:36:00,500 --> 01:36:07,500
Ne znam kuda su je odveli.

833
01:36:09,535 --> 01:36:16,535
Latika.

834
01:36:19,500 --> 01:36:26,500
Otišao sam na show jer
sam mislio da ce ona gledati.

835
01:36:37,500 --> 01:36:42,500
Jamal Malik, neobrazovani 18-godišnjak
decko iz sirotinjskog kraja Mumbaya,

836
01:36:42,535 --> 01:36:46,465
jedan je korak od dobitka,

837
01:36:46,500 --> 01:36:49,465
i ljudi oko mene postavljaju
još jedno vece pitanje:

838
01:36:49,500 --> 01:36:56,500
Da li ce se vratiti veceras
na borbu za 20 miliona rupija?

839
01:37:29,535 --> 01:37:35,500
Hej, daj mi pusu.

840
01:37:35,535 --> 01:37:42,465
Hajde, devojko!

841
01:37:42,500 --> 01:37:46,500
Da, ne mogu ništa cuti od buke.

842
01:37:46,635 --> 01:37:48,565
Moraš nas vratiti u grad.

843
01:37:55,500 --> 01:37:59,500
Kao da nije bilo dovoljno drame
na putu do zadnjeg pitanja...

844
01:37:59,535 --> 01:38:04,500
Jamal Malik je sinoc uhapšen
zbog sumnje na prevaru.

845
01:38:04,535 --> 01:38:11,535
Taj decko. Pametan je.

846
01:38:13,535 --> 01:38:20,535
Ludi "chudge".

847
01:38:22,535 --> 01:38:25,017
Evo, hajde.

848
01:38:25,052 --> 01:38:27,465
Ali...

849
01:38:27,500 --> 01:38:34,500
Samo vozi.
Nece biti druge prilike.

850
01:38:36,535 --> 01:38:43,465
Ubice te.

851
01:38:43,500 --> 01:38:50,500
Ja cu se pobrinuti za njega.

852
01:38:50,535 --> 01:38:55,535
Salim, ne mogu.

853
01:38:56,752 --> 01:38:58,652
Moraš.

854
01:39:05,311 --> 01:39:12,311
Moraš ovo napraviti.

855
01:39:12,500 --> 01:39:19,500
Za sve što sam napravio...
molim te, oprosti mi.

856
01:39:27,535 --> 01:39:34,535
Imaj dobar život.

857
01:40:00,500 --> 01:40:07,500
Vracaš se u show.

858
01:40:32,535 --> 01:40:39,535
Hajde!

859
01:40:51,500 --> 01:40:55,465
Jamal? Milioner?

860
01:40:55,500 --> 01:41:02,500
Multi-milioner?
Onaj sa svom onom gotovinom?

861
01:41:02,535 --> 01:41:08,500
Hajde, idi sa mojim
blagoslovom i osvoji sve.

862
01:41:08,535 --> 01:41:13,465
Volimo te, Jamal!

863
01:41:13,500 --> 01:41:16,465
Naciju je ulovila milionerska
groznica.

864
01:41:16,500 --> 01:41:20,500
Jamal Malik, neobrazovani decko
iz sirotinjskog kraja Mumbaya,

865
01:41:20,535 --> 01:41:23,833
je osvojio 10 milijuna rupija

866
01:41:23,868 --> 01:41:26,343
na kvizu "ko želi biti milioner",

867
01:41:27,500 --> 01:41:30,500
i oko 90 miliona ljudi nas
veceras gleda

868
01:41:30,501 --> 01:41:34,501
da bi videlo da li ce uspeti
osvojiti 20 miliona rupija.

869
01:42:01,536 --> 01:42:03,500
Gde su svi? Vrati se ovamo!

870
01:42:03,535 --> 01:42:09,500
Vratite se na posao!

871
01:42:09,535 --> 01:42:16,535
Poslužitelju?

872
01:42:32,500 --> 01:42:37,500
Dobro došli natrag u
"ko želi biti milioner".

873
01:42:37,535 --> 01:42:39,465
Mogu sa sigurnošću reci
da je veceras

874
01:42:39,500 --> 01:42:43,465
najveca noc u životima
nas dvojice.

875
01:42:43,500 --> 01:42:46,500
Jamal Malik, radnik iz Mumbaya,

876
01:42:46,535 --> 01:42:48,465
je vec osvojio 10 milijuna.

877
01:42:48,500 --> 01:42:50,465
Može otici sa tom
svotom u džepu,

878
01:42:50,500 --> 01:42:53,500
ili napraviti najvece kockanje
u istoriji televizije.

879
01:42:53,535 --> 01:42:55,465
Može odgovarati na
finalno pitanje

880
01:42:55,500 --> 01:43:00,500
i pokušati osvojiti
20 miliona rupija.

881
01:43:00,535 --> 01:43:05,500
Da li si spreman za to pitanje?

882
01:43:05,535 --> 01:43:07,577
Da. -Jamal!

883
01:43:21,440 --> 01:43:23,830
Da li puno citaš, Jamal?

884
01:43:25,798 --> 01:43:27,768
Znam citati.

885
01:43:28,500 --> 01:43:31,465
Sretnice.

886
01:43:31,500 --> 01:43:37,500
U knjizi Alexandra Dumasa,
"Tri musketara",

887
01:43:37,535 --> 01:43:43,500
dva musketara su se zvala
Athos i Porthos.

888
01:43:43,535 --> 01:43:47,500
Koje je bilo ime treceg musketara?

889
01:43:47,535 --> 01:43:50,465
A: Aramis

890
01:43:50,500 --> 01:43:54,500
B: Kardinal Richelieu

891
01:43:54,535 --> 01:43:59,517
C: D'Artagnan

892
01:43:59,552 --> 01:44:04,465
D: Planchet

893
01:44:04,500 --> 01:44:07,465
Ona bi mogla biti treci musketar.

894
01:44:07,500 --> 01:44:10,500
Finalno pitanje za 20 miliona
rupija, i on se smeje.

895
01:44:10,535 --> 01:44:14,017
Mislim da znaš odgovor.

896
01:44:14,052 --> 01:44:17,500
Veruješ li, ja ne verujem.

897
01:44:17,535 --> 01:44:20,465
Ne znaš?

898
01:44:20,500 --> 01:44:25,500
Znaci uzeceš 10 miliona i otici?

899
01:44:25,535 --> 01:44:31,465
Ne. Igracu.

900
01:44:31,500 --> 01:44:33,465
Da te podsetim, Jamal.

901
01:44:33,500 --> 01:44:36,500
Ako pogrešno odgovoriš,

902
01:44:36,535 --> 01:44:39,465
sve ceš izgubiti.

903
01:44:39,500 --> 01:44:43,500
10 miliona rupija, Jamal.

904
01:44:43,535 --> 01:44:47,465
To je sudbina.

905
01:44:47,500 --> 01:44:51,000
Želeo bih nazvati prijatelja.

906
01:44:51,035 --> 01:44:54,465
Idemo na vezu.

907
01:44:54,500 --> 01:45:01,500
Zadnja pomoc. Evo ga.

908
01:45:05,535 --> 01:45:10,017
Zvoni!

909
01:45:10,052 --> 01:45:14,465
ko je?

910
01:45:14,500 --> 01:45:20,465
To je broj moga brata, ali...

911
01:45:20,500 --> 01:45:26,500
Brata koji nije kraj telefona
na pitanju za 20 miliona rupija?

912
01:45:26,535 --> 01:45:33,535
To je jedini broj koji znam.

913
01:45:56,352 --> 01:45:58,052
Sada si sam sa sobom, Jamal.

914
01:46:01,535 --> 01:46:07,465
Halo?

915
01:46:07,500 --> 01:46:10,465
Halo, Jamal?

916
01:46:10,500 --> 01:46:15,500
Mislim da to nije tvoj brat.

917
01:46:15,535 --> 01:46:17,465
To je...

918
01:46:17,500 --> 01:46:18,500
Moje ime je Latika.

919
01:46:18,535 --> 01:46:20,465
Ok, Latika.

920
01:46:20,500 --> 01:46:25,500
Želiš li još jednom cuti pitanje?
I da rašcistimo...

921
01:46:25,535 --> 01:46:31,500
20 miliona rupija za ovaj
odgovor, imate 30 sekundi.

922
01:46:31,535 --> 01:46:38,500
Jamal, molim te
da procitaš pitanje Latiki.

923
01:46:38,535 --> 01:46:41,465
To si stvarno ti? -Da.

924
01:46:41,500 --> 01:46:45,465
Pitanje, Jamal. Pitanje!

925
01:46:45,500 --> 01:46:48,000
U knjizi Alexandra Dumasa,
"Tri musketara",

926
01:46:48,035 --> 01:46:50,500
dva musketara su se zvala
Athos i Porthos.

927
01:46:50,535 --> 01:46:52,465
Koje je bilo ime treceg musketara?

928
01:46:52,500 --> 01:46:59,500
Da li je to A: Aramis, B: Kardinal
Richelieu, C: D'Artagnan ili D: Planchet?

929
01:46:59,535 --> 01:47:01,517
15 sekundi!

930
01:47:01,552 --> 01:47:03,526
Gde si?

931
01:47:03,561 --> 01:47:05,530
Na sigurnom sam.

932
01:47:05,565 --> 01:47:07,465
10 sekundi!

933
01:47:07,500 --> 01:47:13,465
Latika, o cemu razmišljaš?

934
01:47:13,500 --> 01:47:19,500
Ne znam. Nikada ne znam.

935
01:47:19,535 --> 01:47:26,535
Jamal, bez novca...

936
01:47:30,500 --> 01:47:35,500
Sada si prepušten
sam sebi, Jamal.

937
01:47:35,735 --> 01:47:40,035
Tvoj zadnji odgovor
za 20 miliona rupija.

938
01:47:51,535 --> 01:47:55,465
A.

939
01:47:55,500 --> 01:47:58,465
A, zato jer...?

940
01:47:58,500 --> 01:48:01,510
Samo... zato.

941
01:48:02,223 --> 01:48:03,566
Hej, Salim!

942
01:48:07,500 --> 01:48:10,465
Zadnji odgovor?

943
01:48:10,500 --> 01:48:16,500
Da, zadnji odgovor. A, Aramis.

944
01:48:17,035 --> 01:48:20,035
Kompjuter, A.

945
01:48:27,500 --> 01:48:32,500
Jamal Malik, radnik iz Mumbaya,

946
01:48:32,535 --> 01:48:35,465
poslužitelj,

947
01:48:35,500 --> 01:48:38,465
u pitanju za 20 miliona rupija

948
01:48:38,500 --> 01:48:45,500
bio si pitan kako se zvao treci
musketar u noveli Alexandera Dumasa.

949
01:48:45,535 --> 01:48:52,465
Ti si odgovorio A, Aramis.

950
01:48:52,500 --> 01:48:55,500
Što je, moram ti reci...

951
01:48:55,535 --> 01:49:02,535
Tacan odgovor!

952
01:49:22,535 --> 01:49:29,517
Jamal Malik!

953
01:49:29,552 --> 01:49:33,552
Bog je super.

954
01:49:36,761 --> 01:49:38,561
Koja noc!

955
01:52:12,500 --> 01:52:15,465
